-- Icahn Extends Offer for Lions Gate Entertainment Shares Until Nov. 22
-- B y   P h i l   K o h n
-- 2010-11-12T14:13:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-12/icahn-extends-offer-for-lions-gate-entertainment-shares-until-nov-22.html
Carl Icahn said that the offer by
his affiliated entities to purchase up to all of the outstanding
common shares of Lions Gate Entertainment Corp. for $7.50 a
share in cash has been extended, and will now expire at 11:59
p.m., Vancouver time, on November 22, unless further extended or
withdrawn. The offer was contained in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Kohn at 
 pkohn@bloomberg.net  